{"tid":1388102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做咩比籍口班狗衝出黎？求解答愚見","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T16:33:45.000Z","uid":143642,"like":15,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"41382eaa0813aeadac582f722514cc6bfa565d68","tid":1388102,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:52:56.000Z","msg":"我唔撚明 大家掟嘢做咩？射激光做咩？<br />\n發洩？阻狗錄片？<br />\n今次行動唔係為義士打氣？<br />\n等佢知道自己唔係得自己一個？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">點解要比籍口佢地遲放/打人</span><br />\n我知大家情緒好激動<br />\n但有冇諗過義士家屬同朋友感受<br />\n佢地只係想快啲見到屋企人<br />\n你又知唔知好多人都係出黎聲援<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好多人都冇裝備架</span><br />\n我知班狗係癲係仆街 <br />\n你可能話你唔咁做都會照打人照玩野<br />\n但咁多傳媒係到 佢冇籍口同難啲咁樣做<br />\n<br />\n唔啱聽屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">留力聽日東區裁判法院</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"c75bbcd61b0aeaebc3b5a8d27e24632f7fa36254","tid":1388102,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:53:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b8e8a402d537f88d7429c57e48ca510cb231a44","tid":1388102,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:53:28.000Z","msg":"講下你點睇"},{"pid":"47e119e2147810da5942210158aeb78b90883bcc","tid":1388102,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98eb1b79ba32fa3f7ab3c205b178a0779067bd10","tid":1388102,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:53:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13fa0d71fc57596becd60a4d2ce13d4279087497","tid":1388102,"uid":169865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:54:00.000Z","msg":"聽朝法院門口見"},{"pid":"f977e2f549fa0780c69ad7339a1f1ab47aeda836","tid":1388102,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"一個都不能少"},{"pid":"08020baeeb93a923fd676bbb676038bc1b3375eb","